==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Acidic
<hw>A*cid"ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Containing a high percentage of silica; -- opposed to
<ant>basic</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>of or relating to acid; having the character of an
acid, <as>as an <ex>acidic</ex> solution</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Acidiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
